# Kamailio dispatcher destination list for Llamenos
#
# Format: <set_id> <destination_uri> [flags] [priority] [attrs]
#
# Group 1: Asterisk PBX backends
# Add one line per Asterisk instance for load balancing / failover.
#
# In Docker Compose, asterisk resolves to the asterisk container.
# SIP UDP on port 5060.

1 sip:asterisk:5060 0 0
